Elissa Landi https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elissa_Landi 0 Elissa Landi (born Elisabeth Marie Christine Kühnelt, December 6, 1904 – October 21, 1948) was an Italian-born Austrian actress who was popular in Hollywood films of the 1920s and 1930s. She was noted for her aristocratic bearing.
